{"word":"συμμεθίστημι","slug":"συμμεθίστημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμμεθίστημι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to help in changing</i>, 3rd sg. <el>συμμεθιστᾷ</el> (from <el>-ιστάω</el>) <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 et <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to change places along with</i> another, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}